[SN]TITLE[SN]
Drone regulations 'need enforcing', says video boss

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Commercial drone sales are expected to almost double in 2016. But is the industry properly regulated?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
20 April 2016 Last updated at 13:40 BST
The drone video marketplace Airstoc has 5,000 operators in over 100 countries.
Its chief executive, Giles Moore, says regulations surrounding drone flights need to be enforced.
